# AGENTS

This file serves as a context guide for AI agents working on the Sudoku Game project.

## Project Overview
**Name:** Sudoku Game (Brutalist Edition)
**Platform:** iOS (primary), Android (optional)
**Stack:** Expo (React Native), TypeScript, React Native Skia, Reanimated, Moti.
**Design:** Brutalist, Black & White, Offline-first.

## Core Principles
1. **Offline-First:** No internet dependency for core gameplay. JSON-based puzzles.
2. **Performance:** 60fps animations via Skia and Reanimated.
3. **Aesthetics:** Strict brutalist design. High contrast. No default UI elements.
4. **Monetization:** AdMob (Rewarded, Interstitial, Banner) + RevenueCat (Ad-Free Subscription).

## Tech Stack Details
- **Framework:** Expo (Managed Workflow)
- **Graphics:** @shopify/react-native-skia (Canvas rendering for board, notes, effects)
- **Animations:** react-native-reanimated, moti
- **Navigation:** expo-router (preferred) or react-navigation
- **Storage:** expo-secure-store (Identity), @react-native-async-storage/async-storage (Game Data)
- **Ads:** react-native-google-mobile-ads
- **IAP:** react-native-purchases (RevenueCat)

## Key Directories (Planned)
- `/src/components`: UI components (BrutalistButton, NumberPad, etc.)
- `/src/game`: Game logic (Sudoku engine, generator, validator)
- `/src/screens`: App screens
- `/src/assets`: Fonts, JSON puzzles
- `/src/context`: State management (GameContext, ThemeContext)

## Agent Persona
You are a senior React Native engineer with a focus on high-performance graphics and strict design implementation. You prioritize code cleanliness, type safety (TypeScript), and smooth animations.
